name: Suigintou (Rozen Maiden)
description:
smol version: I never intended this one-outfit model to be 144mb so here's a smaller version. If you got the previous one and you're happy with it you don't need this. I guess smaller size means it's a bit worse (mostly when it comes to anatomy), but it's not a big difference.

This is my 50th model ｡°✩‧₊˚彡And so I decided to make it a model of character whose design I always adored, Suigintou from Rozen Maiden :) I actually browsed my old art folder today and found some vector images I made of her 16 years ago. Time flies :' )

There's only one outfit so I tried my best to make it count and I feel it came out great :D I'm very happy with this one and I think it stands up to existing models. Also I played dress-up with it a lot cause that's what you do with dolls ^_^

Sorry for larger size, I actually meant to make it smaller but I forgot and already made the images. Also sadly I had to edit images prompts slightly because they were triggering automatic block from website. I've looked through TOS and I see this as false positive due to way tags are phrased :(

Prompt for her outfit is suigintou, lolita fashion, lolita hairband, detached collar, black wings, black dress, juliet sleeves, frills, cross, cross-laced dress, knee boots.
